graph.api

Interface Node<T,U extends java.lang.Comparable<?>>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NodeImpl

    public interface Node<T,U extends java.lang.Comparable<?>>
    Represents the core data structure that will make up the main Graph component. Designed to be generic but still adhere to standard graph properties for genericized Graph creation.
